{"tid":2039341,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"著名對沖基金經理阿克曼旗下基金公司沽清所持巴郡股份","createTime":"2020-05-28T03:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T04:14:54.000Z","uid":289259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a6218a7ddfa750adc319cd08a1429c179518ef","tid":2039341,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"綜合媒體報道，美國著名對沖基金經理阿克曼(Bill Ackman)旗下Pershing Square Capital Management，已全數沽售所持巴郡股份。公司在電話會議上披露有關沽售，並套取現金投資更快取得及更高回報的項目上。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，目前市況已與一年前投資巴郡股份有很大分別，認為巴郡長期投資表現非常強勁，但認為目前環境意味有更多機會作出高回報投資。公司截至3月底止共持有10億美元巴郡股份。<br />\n<br />\n巴郡沽人<br />\n人沽巴郡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735e606607697fc27d6f905ba224a3ebd12b8f9e","tid":2039341,"uid":105166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"點解Ackman條傻仔仲有錢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲未收皮咩？條on9之前狙擊康寶萊輸10億美金，前期做preparation已經洗幾千萬美金，宜家大賺硬，呢場輸仗輸到佢出晒名㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢又沽巴郡，唔知結果會點呢？"},{"pid":"7142c4429c41bd95c8cef8848450dfad74df7fa1","tid":2039341,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"735e606607697fc27d6f905ba224a3ebd12b8f9e","tid":2039341,"uid":105166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"點解Ackman條傻仔仲有錢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲未收皮咩？條on9之前狙擊康寶萊輸10億美金，前期做preparation已經洗幾千萬美金，宜家大賺硬，呢場輸仗輸到佢出晒名㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢又沽巴郡，唔知結果會點呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"佢唔係沽廢老<br />\n係清倉廢老持有既股<br />\n嫌跑得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas